<br>
If my participation was measured but never rewarded, then I view RPP as a failure.  Never mind the fact that my character who is raiding can't use the item directly to have fun.  Me the person can.  I have a character I could give it to that would have a great time with it!!  I put in the time.  I contributed to the guild.  I was rewarded.  <br>
